Title: Relates to the establishment of a community renewable energy program
Summary: Relates to the establishment of a community renewable energy program; directs the public service commission to evaluate a program to allow individuals to choose to receive energy generated from renewable energy systems.
LawCode: Add ยง66-u, Pub Serv L
ActClause: AN ACT to amend the public service law, in relation to the establishment of a community renewable energy program
